0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534590\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534590\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 07, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zsp1665702996195.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zsp1665702996195.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zsp1665702996195.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zsp1665702996195\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Start and Test the WRD\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You start and test the WRD from an administration page.</p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__context_w1332ab1b5b1_w1333ab1b5_w1334ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__p_d66851e1_d66852e1_d66853e1\">After creating the and deploying the <span class=\"ph filepath\">wrd.war</span> file, use the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">IBM Web Administration for i</span> page to start the WRD.</p>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__li_d29411e1_d29412e1_d29413e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__p_d66854e1_d66855e1_d66856e1\">On the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">IBM Web Administration for\n                  i</span> page, select the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Manage</span> tab. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">There are four additional tabs under the top tabs.</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__li_d29414e1_d29415e1_d29416e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Select the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Application Servers</span> tab.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__li_d29417e1_d29418e1_d29419e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">In the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Server:</span> drop-down list (beneath the tabs), select the application server you have just created.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__li_d29420e1_d29421e1_d29422e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">If this application server is not running, click the green 'Play' button on the left to start the application server. Wait until the word <code class=\"ph codeph\">Running</code> appears to the left of the green button.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__li_d29423e1_d29424e1_d29425e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__p_d66857e1_d66858e1_d66859e1\">In the left pane, under\n                  <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Applications</span>, click <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Manage Installed\n                  Applications</span>. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">On the right side, a list of installed applications is displayed. Among them is\n               the WRD, listed by the name you gave it when you installed it. If it has status\n                  <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Running</span> you can skip the next step, otherwise the WRD must\n               be started.</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__li_d29426e1_d29427e1_d29428e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__p_d66860e1_d66861e1_d66862e1\">Select the WRD application and click\n                  <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Start</span>. </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__note_w1335ab1b5b3c11b3b1_w1336ab1b5b3c11b3_w1337ab1b5b3c11_w1338ab1b5b3_w1339ab1b5_w1340ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Start</span> button is dimmed, then the\n                     <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Enablement</span> field tells you whether it has been started.\n                  If the field is enabled, it was started. Enabled applications start when the\n                  application server itself starts.</div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__li_d29429e1_d29430e1_d29431e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__p_d66863e1_d66864e1_d66865e1\">If you left the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">TESTABLE</span>\n               servlet setting to <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code> in <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnb1665702995328.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnb1665702995328.html\" title=\"The IBM Integrated Web application server for i can deploy applications that are in the form of a web archive file, .war file or a web application bundle .wab file. The Uniface Web Request Dispatcher (WRD) servlet is not in this format, so it must be packaged into a .war file.\">Configure the WRD and Create a wrd.war File on iSeries</a>, you\n               can start another browser and enter the following URL: </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">http://<var class=\"keyword varname\">iSeriesNetworkName</var>:<var class=\"keyword varname\">PortNumber</var>/<var class=\"keyword varname\">ContextRoot</var>/wrd/run/WRD_Version</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">for example,</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">http://myas400:10000/uniface/wrd/run/WRD_Version</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__li_d29432e1_d29433e1_d29434e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">PortNumber</var>—port number\n                     you supplied in <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"chy1665702996121.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/chy1665702996121.html\" title=\"You create new application servers on a valid local host.\">Create a New Application Server</a>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__li_d29435e1_d29436e1_d29437e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ContextRoot</var>—context root\n                     you supplied in <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mlx1665702995827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mlx1665702995827.html\" title=\"You can now deploy the WAR file (wrd.war) you created earlier. See Configure the WRD and Create a wrd.war File on iSeries.\">Install the WRD in the Application Server</a>. </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__p_d66866e1_d66867e1_d66868e1\">After a few seconds, you should see the Uniface\n                  Test Middleware response page. This indicates that the WRD and the application\n                  server are configured correctly.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zsp1665702996195__p_d66869e1_d66870e1_d66871e1\">If you forgot what the context root or the port\n                  number is, you can click the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Properties</span> button and select\n                  the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Context Root Port Mapping</span> tab to find out.</p>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534590\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534590\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Start and Test the WRD Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 07, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Start and Test the WRD You start and test the WRD from an administration page. After creating the and deploying the wrd.war file, use the IBM Web Administration for i page to start the WRD. On the IBM Web Administration for i page, select the Manage tab. There are four additional tabs under the top tabs. Select the Application Servers tab. In the Server: drop-down list (beneath the tabs), select the application server you have just created. If this application server is not running, click the green 'Play' button on the left to start the application server. Wait until the word Running appears to the left of the green button. In the left pane, under Applications , click Manage Installed Applications . On the right side, a list of installed applications is displayed. Among them is the WRD, listed by the name you gave it when you installed it. If it has status Running you can skip the next step, otherwise the WRD must be started. Select the WRD application and click Start . Note: If the Start button is dimmed, then the Enablement field tells you whether it has been started. If the field is enabled, it was started. Enabled applications start when the application server itself starts. If you left the TESTABLE servlet setting to true in Configure the WRD and Create a wrd.war File on iSeries , you can start another browser and enter the following URL: http:// iSeriesNetworkName : PortNumber / ContextRoot /wrd/run/WRD_Version Copy for example, http://myas400:10000/uniface/wrd/run/WRD_Version Copy PortNumber —port number you supplied in Create a New Application Server . ContextRoot —context root you supplied in Install the WRD in the Application Server . After a few seconds, you should see the Uniface Test Middleware response page. This indicates that the WRD and the application server are configured correctly. If you forgot what the context root or the port number is, you can click the Properties button and select the Context Root Port Mapping tab to find out. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}